  "keyFeatures": [
    "Bidirectional routing — parse URLs into typed values and print them back to URLs",
    "Type-safe route modeling with Swift enums",
    "Composable parsers using result builders for path, query, headers, body, and cookies",
    "URLRoutingClient for making type-safe API requests from iOS/macOS apps",
    "Deep linking support for iOS applications",
    "Server-side routing support with Vapor integration",
    "Built on swift-parsing for composable, invertible parser-printers",
    "Support for HTTP methods, schemes, hosts, fragments, and form data"
  ],
